      ],
      "plan": [
        "Trace config load/merge path for `WebhookConfig` and where URL is first considered valid.",
        "Review `/tmp/ralph-codebase-audit.md` security subsection and Quick win #2 if available.",
        "Design allowlist/default-HTTPS policy and config knob if needed (align with schema + docs patterns).",
        "Implement URL validation with tests covering loopback, link-local, and acceptable HTTPS cases.",
        "Run `cargo test -p ralph` for affected modules."
      ],
      "notes": [
        "HTTPS-only default; optional http + private-target opt-ins",
