      "request": "Cross-surface coherence (RalphMac error handling): Several machine subprocess helpers (e.g. Workspace+Decompose runTaskDecompose) surface raw stderr on failure, while Workspace+TaskMutations already decodes MachineErrorDocument from stderr for classification (taskConflict). When the CLI fails with the versioned machine_error JSON document on stderr, Mac users see opaque JSON instead of code/message/retryable. Acceptance: unify decoding so machine command failures in RalphCore prefer MachineErrorDocument when present (decompose, queue recovery helpers, any runAndCollect machine paths that still stringify stderr); keep behavior aligned with docs/machine-contract.md machine_error section.",
